tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE stock_levels (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  product_id INT,
  stock_quantity INT,
  last_updated TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE demand_data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  product_id INT,
  demand_quantity INT,
  demand_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE DemandData (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    demand_level INT,
    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE InventoryAnalysis (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    optimal_stock INT,
    reorder_quantity INT,
    last_analysis_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE stock_levels (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    quantity INT,
    min_stock_level INT,
    max_stock_level INT
);

CREATE TABLE demand_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    demand_level INT,
    forecasted_demand INT,
    demand_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE inventory_analysis (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    analysis_date DATE,
    restock_recommendation VARCHAR(255),
    analysis_result TEXT
);
